Maryland Casualty Company, a Corporation, Plaintiff in Error v. H. J. Stewart as Receiver for Permenter State Bank, Defendant in Error. A Writ of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Alachua. Hampton & Hampton, for Plaintiff in Error;

Writ of Error dismissed on praecipe of counsel for plaintiff in error.

No appearance for Defendant in Error.
